<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 00:56:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市低迷，未来存在大量事件风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-15/</link><description>执政党在台湾获胜的反应有限，基本上维持了现状。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 00:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>王毅：中方呼吁召开更大规模和平会议解决加沙危机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-calls-larger-scale-peace-conference-gaza-crisis-wang-yi-2024-01-15/</link><description>中国外长王毅表示，加沙战事持续升级，中方呼吁召开更大规模、更权威、更有效的国际和平会议，并制定落实两国方案的具体时间表。</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 00:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-calls-larger-scale-peace-conference-gaza-crisis-wang-yi-2024-01-15/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国军方和政府不顾美国禁令采购英伟达芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-military-government-acquire-nvidia-chips-despite-us-ban-2024-01-14/</link><description>Nvidia 构建的图形处理单元被认为优于 AI 工作的竞争对手产品，因为它们可以更有效地处理机器学习任务所需的大量数据。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 23:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-military-government-acquire-nvidia-chips-despite-us-ban-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>瑞士外交官表示，结束乌克兰战争需要俄罗斯的盟友中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/top-diplomats-meet-davos-ukraine-peace-formula-2024-01-14/</link><description>乌克兰在达沃斯世界经济论坛上召开了来自世界各地的国家安全顾问会议，推动其和平方案结束与俄罗斯近两年的战争。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 12:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/top-diplomats-meet-davos-ukraine-peace-formula-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾大选让世界市场松了一口气，但令当地投资者担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-election-relief-world-markets-concern-local-investors-2024-01-14/</link><description>台湾大选可能会缓解全球对台湾与中国关系的担忧，同时引发周一国内股市小幅抛售，因为投资者担心选举结果可能会阻碍经济政策。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 08:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-election-relief-world-markets-concern-local-investors-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国外交官谴责外国政府就台湾大选后发表的言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassies-condemn-foreign-officials-over-taiwan-post-election-remarks-2024-01-14/</link><description>中国外交部及其驻世界各地的大使馆谴责外国政府在周六选举后祝贺台湾民进党及其当选总统赖清德。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-embassies-condemn-foreign-officials-over-taiwan-post-election-remarks-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国前官员将访问台湾进行大选后会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-us-officials-visit-taiwan-post-election-talks-2024-01-14/</link><description>美国驻台北事实上的大使馆表示，两名前美国高级官员将于周日抵达台湾进行选举后会谈，并强调美国政府对台海和平的“长期利益”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 07:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-us-officials-visit-taiwan-post-election-talks-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新总统面临中国压力，未获得多数席位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-new-president-faces-tough-time-with-china-pressure-no-parliament-2024-01-14/</link><description>赖清德虽然以不到一半的选票以微弱优势获胜，但他的政党失去了对议会的控制权，当选总统将不得不依靠议会来通过立法和支出。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 06:20:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwans-new-president-faces-tough-time-with-china-pressure-no-parliament-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>中方反对日方向台湾当选总统贺电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japans-congratulatory-message-taiwan-president-elect-2024-01-14/</link><description>中国驻日本大使馆周日表示，“坚决反对”日本外务大臣上川洋子祝贺台湾新当选总统赖清德的声明。</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 04:19:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-opposes-japans-congratulatory-message-taiwan-president-elect-2024-01-14/</guid></item><item><title>台湾新当选总统赖清德将面临中国的愤怒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-president-elect-lai-face-chinas-ire-after-victory-2024-01-13/</link><description>赖在竞选期间多次表示，他希望与中国保持现状，并提出与北京对话。但在北京看来，他是一个分裂主义者，是一个“彻头彻尾的麻烦制造者”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 13:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/taiwan-president-elect-lai-face-chinas-ire-after-victory-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>西藏不是焦点，镇压持续存在：流亡前领导人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tibetan-issues-not-focus-repression-persists-exiled-former-leader-2024-01-13/</link><description>西藏流亡政府前领导人周六表示，国际上对西藏困境的讨论越来越少，但镇压仍在继续，中国正在将其在其他地区的做法应用到其他地区。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 07:22:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/tibetan-issues-not-focus-repression-persists-exiled-former-leader-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯与中国官员讨论人权、台海问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-raises-human-rights-issues-meeting-with-senior-chinese-official-2024-01-13/</link><description>美国国务院表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周五在华盛顿会见中国高级官员刘建超时表达了对中国人权问题的担忧，并补充说，他们还讨论了“维护台湾海峡的和平与稳定”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 00:50:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-raises-human-rights-issues-meeting-with-senior-chinese-official-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>台湾选民拒绝中国，执政党获得第三个总统任期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/polls-open-taiwans-critical-elections-watched-closely-by-china-2024-01-13/</link><description>赖清德领导的政党主张台湾的独立身份，拒绝中国的领土主张，正在寻求第三次连任。北京将这次选举视为战争与和平之间的选择。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 00:06:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/polls-open-taiwans-critical-elections-watched-closely-by-china-2024-01-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促加强房地产业融资协调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-better-financing-coordination-housing-sector-2024-01-12/</link><description>在政策制定者努力重振低迷的房地产市场之际，中国住房和城乡建设部和金融监管机构要求地方政府更好地与金融机构协调，为房地产项目提供融资支持。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-better-financing-coordination-housing-sector-2024-01-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国2023年银行贷款创历史新高，但经济仍举步维艰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-2023-bank-lending-record-high-economy-still-struggling-2024-01-12/</link><description>12 月份中国新增银行贷款增幅低于预期，但由于央行保持宽松政策以支持意外不稳定的经济复苏，2023 年贷款创下新纪录。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 11:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-2023-bank-lending-record-high-economy-still-struggling-2024-01-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>